Greenville.WWOK-LP:
WWOK-LP (95.3 FM) is a non-commercial LPFM radio station located in Greenville, South Carolina, that features Easy Listening music. The station is licensed by the FCC to broadcast with an ERP of .001 kW.


== Station history ==
WWOK-LP signed on February 5, 2004. It is owned by Missionary Broadcasters Inc.
